quran[28]{c,v,t}:
  30,54,di Mulungu amene adakulengani inu ofoka ndipo adakupatsani mphamvu pambuyo pa kufoka. Ndipo atakupatsani mphamvu adakupatsani kufoka ndi imvi. Iye amalenga chilichonse chimene wafuna ndipo ndiye amene amadziwa zonse ndipo ndiye Mwini mphamvu
  30,55,"Ndipo pamene ola lidzadza, anthu ochimwa adzalumbira kuti adangokhala ola limodzi lokha. Kotero iwo amakhala onamizidwa"
  30,56,"Ndipo iwo amene adapatsidwa nzeru ndi chikhulupiriro adzati, “Ndithudi inu mwakhala molingana ndi malamulo a Mulungu mpaka pa tsiku louka kwa akufa. Kotero ili ndilo tsiku louka kwa akufa koma inu simunalidziwe ayi.”"
  30,57,Koma patsiku limeneli zodandaula zawo sizidzawathandiza anthu onse ochimwa ndipo sizidzamveka ayi
  30,58,"Ndithudi m’Buku ili la Korani anthu tawaikiramo zitsanzo zambiri zosiyanasiyana ndipo ngati iwe utawabweretsera chiphunzitso iwo amene sakhulupirira adzati, “Iwe siuli kutsatira china chilichonse koma bodza ndi matsenga.”"
  30,59,Mmenemo ndi mmene Mulungu amatsekera mitima ya anthu osadziwa
  30,60,Kotero pirirani. Lonjezo la Mulungu ndi loona ndipo usalole anthu opanda chikhulupiriro kuti akuderere iwe
  31,1,Alif Lam Mim
  31,2,Awa ndi mawu a m’Buku la nzeru
  31,3,Chilangizo ndi chifundo kwa anthu angwiro
  31,4,"Amene amapemphera nthawi zonse, amene amapereka msonkho wothandiza anthu osauka ndipo amakhulupirira m’moyo umene uli nkudza"
  31,5,Amenewa ndiwo amene atsogozedwa bwino ndi Ambuye wawo ndipo ndithudi adzakhala opambana
  31,6,"Koma pakati pa anthu, alipo ena amene amagula nkhani zopanda pake ndi zopanda tanthauzo ndi cholinga chosocheretsa anthu ku njira ya Mulungu ndi kuipanga iyo kukhala chinthu choseketsa. Awa adzalandira chilango chochititsa manyazi"
  31,7,"Ndipo pamene chivumbulutso chathuchilakatulidwakwaiye, iyeamatembenukamonyada kuoneka ngati kuti sadamve china chilichonse, kapena ngati kuti m’makutu mwake muli phula kotero muuzeni za chilango chowawa"
  31,8,"Akakhala iwo amene akhulupirira ndipo amachita ntchito za bwino, ndithudi, adzakhala ku Paradiso"
  31,9,Kukhalamo mpaka kalekale ndi lonjezo loona la Mulungu. Ndipo Iye ndiye Mwini mphamvu ndipo ndi wanzeru zonse
  31,10,Iye adalenga kumwamba popanda nsanamira monga muonera ndipo adalenga mapiri pa dziko lapansi kuti mwina dziko likhoza kuyenda pamodzi ndi inu. Ndipo m’dzikomo adaikamo nyama za mtundu uliwonse. Ndipo ife timatumiza mvula kuchokera ku mtambo ndipo timameretsa mbewu za mitundu yosiyanasiyana
  31,11,"Ichi ndi chilengedwe cha Mulungu ndipo ndionetseni zimene iwo amene amakhala pafupi naye adalenga. Iyayi, anthu opanda chilungamo ndi olakwa"
  31,12,"Ndithudi Ife tidamupatsa nzeru Luqman ponena kuti, “Thokozani Mulungu. Aliyense amene amathokoza Mulungu, amathokoza chifukwa cha mzimu wake ndipo aliyense amene sathokoza, ndithudi, Mulungu sasowa kanthu ndipo ndi wolemekezeka.”"
  31,13,"Ndi pamene Luqman adamuuza mwana wake adamulangiza kuti, “Mwana wanga usamafanizire Mulungu ndi china chilichonse chifukwa ndi tchimo loopsa.”"
  31,14,"Ndipo Ife timamulamula munthu kuonetsa chifundo kwa makolo ake. Movutika amayi ake adamubereka iye ndipo m’zaka ziwiri adamuyamwitsa. Kotero, thokozani Ine ndiponso thokozani makolo anu chifukwa ndi kwa Ine kumene mudzabwerera"
  31,15,"Koma ngati akuuza kuti uzindifanizira Ine ndi china chake chimene siuchidziwa, usawamvere. Aonetsere chifundo ndipo utsatire zochita za iye amene amalapa kwa Ine ndi kundimvera. Ndipo kwa Ine ndi kumene nonse mudzabwerera ndiponso ndidzakuuzani zonse zimene mudachita"
  31,16,"“oh mwana wanga! Choipa ngakhale chitakhala ngati njere ya mpiru imene idakwiriridwa m’kati mwa mwala kapena kwina kulikonse kumwamba kapena pa dziko lapansi, Mulungu adzachitulutsa. Mulungu ali ndi nzeru ndiponso amadziwa chinthu china chilichonse.”"
  31,17,"“Oh mwana wanga! Limbikira kupemphera, khazikitsa chilungamo ndipo udziletse kuchita zoipa. Khala opirira pa chilichonse chimene chidza pa iwe.” Ndithudi! Awa ndi malamulo ofunika amene adalamula Mulungu ndipo ayenera kutsatidwa"
  31,18,“Usanyodole anthu kapena kuyenda modzitukumula pa dziko. Mulungu sakonda anthu odzitukumula.”
  31,19,“Ndipo uyenera kukhala wofatsa ndipo mawu ako azikhala otsika chifukwa mawu aukali kwambiri ndi kulira kwa bulu.”
  31,20,"Kodi simuona kuti Mulungu wapanga zinthu zimene zili kumwamba ndiponso zimene zili padziko lapansi kukumverani inu ndipo adakupatsani inu zabwino zooneka ndi zosaoneka ndi maso? Ndipo pakati pa anthu pali iye amene amatsutsa zinthu zokhudza Mulungu ngakhale iye sadziwa china chilichonse, kapena chilangizo kapena Buku lopereka muuni"
  31,21,"Ndipo zikanenedwa kwa iwo kuti: Tsatirani zimene Mulungu wavumbulutsa iwo amati, Iyayi. Ife sititsatira china chilichonse koma zokhazo zimene tidapeza makolo athu ali kutsatira. Ngakhale kuti Satana ali kuwaitanira iwo ku chilango cha moto"